{"tid":2128709,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"最強蝸牛係大陸舔共遊戲，唔好課金","createTime":"2020-07-28T06:38:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-31T15:46:39.000Z","uid":193502,"like":58,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"7d1f5d858dd38bc46dea5400cda922c20f0c3d06","tid":2128709,"uid":193502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T06:38:29.000Z","msg":"2020-07-27 06:35:22<br />\n首次上稿 00:51<br />\n更新時間 06:35<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/07/26/phplbUKvR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F07%2F26%2FphplbUKvR.jpg&h=3b7202c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕手機遊戲「最強蝸牛」上線不久便登上熱門下載排行第一名，不過臉書專頁「行走的故事詩/yanwu」指出，遊戲使用大量中國用語，玩家聊天室更實施言論審查，若打反送中、台灣獨立、小熊維尼、六四、蔡英文等詞語會被「符號」擋掉，玩家發言權限甚至可能因此被停15至30天。<br />\n<br />\n根據粉專「行走的故事詩/yanwu」貼文，這款遊戲在網紅與鋪天蓋地的廣告下，推出不久後就榮登Google Play、App store「雙榜」榜首，試玩後也發現非常具遊戲性，畫面可愛、內容詼諧，語言也使用繁體中文，但從介紹、引導到公告都充斥「中國用語」，例如「反饋（台灣稱回饋）」、「萌新（指遊戲新手）」等。<br />\n<br />\n文中寫道，陸陸續續有玩家回報，在聊天室裡如果提到「國共、革命、林鄭月娥、光復香港、台灣獨立、武漢肺炎、六四二十四、言論自由、習維尼、小粉紅」等詞，會顯示成「***」，或是被系統禁止發言。<br />\n<br />\n粉專提到，有苦主因為打了「官方」一詞慘遭禁言；遊戲裡有叫「萬能鑰匙」、「獨立宣言」的道具，「相信我，你打了都會變成***」，形成遊戲道具名稱都不能講的窘境。<br />\n<br />\n「行走的故事詩/yanwu」說，這款手遊明明開了台灣伺服器，卻當作是在中國境內實行言論審查，令人難以接受，目前已刪除遊戲。粉專強調，言論自由是「不守護就可能會默默消失的東西」，希望大家玩遊戲時，不用因為發表任何言論而被審查禁言。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/07/26/phpRg1iyX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F07%2F26%2FphpRg1iyX.jpg&h=bb927106&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀：<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=37563&amp;snA=331\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D37563%26snA%3D331&d=oFI5KSBgBGvHra6dYUznBq%2FFu68%2BWP7gD6%2BC1gzqbK8%3D&h=f0a4171a\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=37563&amp;snA=331</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=37563&amp;snA=621\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D37563%26snA%3D621&d=oFI5KSBgBGvHra6dYUznBq%2FFu68%2BWP7gD6%2BC1gzqbK8%3D&h=20b23fb6\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=37563&amp;snA=621</a>"},{"pid":"ded3cb290197954dbda9758c3a88970dfb8e220a","tid":2128709,"uid":301989,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T06:40:28.000Z","msg":"睇個名都知on9"},{"pid":"a38f5e8e78a8a2e5f073148dcba3f3b7ce2db8f3","tid":2128709,"uid":14494,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T06:43:23.000Z","msg":"以後邊隻驚比我改名做光復香港先會課金<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"198d7d6a16475c630281c1c59853a38232336458","tid":2128709,"uid":61348,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T06:44:38.000Z","msg":"直頭咪玩 仲講課金<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"842916155b04de298035d4e8748657509546521e","tid":2128709,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T06:46:41.000Z","msg":"不了"},{"pid":"720f9ef7d2d233f65b9bf013111195ca5f2dc8e5","tid":2128709,"uid":193502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T06:46:46.000Z","msg":"來源<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3240594\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3240594&d=oFI5KSBgBGvHra6dYUznBq%2FFu68%2BWP7gD6%2BC1gzqbK8%3D&h=96d8d075\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3240594&h=3ab5c452\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3240594</a>"},{"pid":"77bb6b0a15aa225288bb77ed16d5264742cff85f","tid":2128709,"uid":17209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T06:48:44.000Z","msg":"中國製+打壓言論自由，絕對唔應該支持<img src=\"/assets/faces